    <string name="help_credits">
        The goal of VAPORSKULL is to uncover all the skulls on the game board by using the least number of scans possible.
        Selecting a pink cell will either reveal a skull or use a scan to count and display the total number of hidden
        skulls in the row and column. Selecting a revealed skull will also use a scan on the skull. When all skulls are
        revealed, the game is over and you win.
